msgid ""
"The power(s) to which `x` is raised. If `x` contains multiple values, `p` "
"has to either be a scalar, or contain the same number of values as `x`. In "
"the latter case, the result is ``x[0]**p[0], x[1]**p[1], ...``."
msgstr ""

